      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The meat with the milk is the gravy of the Prophets<sup>as</sup>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘ Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Meat with milk is the sauce of Prophets, ‘Alayhim al- Salam. ’” "
        ]
